apture** — The diff format expands from `{property: 'padding', from: 'lg', to: 'md'}` to include structural intents: `{type: 'reorder', parent: 'Stack', children: ['Title', 'Subtitle', 'Body'], newOrder: [1, 0, 2]}`\n4. **Structural preview** — For reordering, either re-render the component (native rendering path) or use CSS `order` as a *temporary* preview hint before finalize applies the real JSX change\n\n**Phasing:**\n- v1: Token editing (spacing, radius, color, font) — current scope\n- v1.5: Layout property editing (`display`, `flex-direction`, `gap`) + component tree view in panel\n- v2: Drag-to-reorder within containers + visibility toggle + intent capture in finalize pipeline",
