          "type": "assistant",
          "text": "**Security review is in** (1 of 5). Key findings:\n\n- **HIGH**: Selector injection in `finalizeDiff` — unescaped `testId` can break out of CSS attribute selector\n- **MEDIUM** (x3): ReDoS in Tailwind bracket regex (`\\[\\S+?\\]`), prototype key collision in themeDefaults lookup, raw component name used as fallback selector\n- Correctly handled: SVG className, `Object.keys` prototype safety\n\nWaiting on 4 more reviewers...",
