for pure functions are valuable but they can't validate cross-system contracts.\n`─────────────────────────────────────────────────`\n\nThe full review is at `tasks/phase3-review.md` with 3 Critical, 9 High, 17 Medium, and 10 Low findings. Want me to start fixing the critical items?",
