          "text": "**JS/TS review** is back — 1 of 5 done. Found 1 HIGH (elementMap eviction fragility with public exposure), 2 MEDIUM (rAF zero-rect flash, .d.ts constant drift), 3 LOW. All fixes verified correct. Waiting on the other 4.",
