lback | 1 line | Prevents (0,0) flash |\n| 5 | PR-M3: Pass `e.data.payload` not `e.data` to handlers | 1 line | Payload isolation for Phase 4 |\n| 6 | PR-CR1: IIFE integration tests | ~12-15 tests | Addresses the single largest gap |\n\nItems 1-5 are one-line changes totaling ~5 minutes of work. Item 6 is the structural investment.\n\n---\n\n## Review Methodology Note\n\nAll 5 reviews were conducted by the same persona panel as the original review, running as Claude Task agents in parallel with direct codebase access. Each agent independently read the updated implementation, type declarations, test suite, and the original review findings. Findings were consolidated by deduplication and cross-referencing. The prototype pollution consensus (PR-H1/PR-H2) was independently flagged by all 4 code-reviewing personas.",
